We need more volunteers interested in presenting. If interested please contact me. We are just collecting  people who are interested at this time. We will try to let you know if you are selected soon after. Topics can be on API use or building for the CMS - basically anything HubSpot development related.

I can say from speaking at HubSpot’s developer day 2018 it was a purely positive experience for both myself and my company. We are still getting new clients almost a year later because people watch the video with my talk in it.

Date Sept 3rd. morning and mid day(BEFORE club inbound). Location is somewhere awesome in HubSpot’s HQ(Their offices, not the HubSpot location inside club Inbound). More specific details coming soon.
